{"id": 62617, "date": "2025-11-30T04:00:43", "date_gmt": "2025-11-30T12:00:43", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=62617"}, "modified": "2026-07-01T11:58:02", "modified_gmt": "2026-07-01T18:58:02", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-november-30-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/30/kingdom-of-days-november-30-2/", "title": {"rendered": "November 30"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1953:\u00a0</strong>Original E Street Band member David Sancious is born in Asbury Park, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled show at Virginia Commonwealth University in Richmond is postponed to January.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at the War Memorial Theater in Trenton.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>At The Record Plant in New York City, Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;Racing in the Street.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes the River Tour to the Civic Arena in Pittsburgh, where Bruce dedicates &#8220;The Promised Land&#8221; to Joe Grushecky.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I1Ab0iyJitA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14352\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o.jpg?fit=387%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"387,546\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"32516974517_f2dba9430d_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o.jpg?fit=387%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14352 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o.jpg?resize=387%2C546&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"387\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o.jpg?w=387&amp;ssl=1 387w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/32516974517_f2dba9430d_o.jpg?resize=213%2C300&amp;ssl=1 213w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;Roll Away the Stone,&#8221; &#8220;Swoop Man,&#8221; and &#8220;Under the Big Sky,&#8221; all of which remain unreleased to this day.</p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at The Summit in Houston on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2IEIBCk4wKo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>On this week&#8217;s episode of <em>American Top 40,\u00a0</em>host Casey Kasem introduces Clarence&#8217;s new single with the story of how The Boss and The Big Man first met.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-62617-7\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/AT40-1985-11-30.mp3?_=7\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/AT40-1985-11-30.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/AT40-1985-11-30.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new touring band bring World Tour 1992 to The Omni in Atlanta.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cjOiRN382kg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22899\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1992-11-30a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?fit=1669%2C796&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1669,796\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1992-11-30a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?fit=758%2C361&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22899 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?resize=758%2C362&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?w=1669&amp;ssl=1 1669w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?resize=1024%2C488&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?resize=768%2C366&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30a.png?resize=1536%2C733&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22900\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1992-11-30b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30b.png?fit=201%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"201,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1992-11-30b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30b.png?fit=118%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22900 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1992-11-30b.png?resize=201%2C1748&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"201\" height=\"1748\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his second of two nights at the Berkeley Community Theater, where &#8220;The New Timer&#8221; makes its debut, and the setlist contains the entire\u00a0<em>The Ghost of Tom Joad</em> album. Once again, John Wesley Harding opens the show with a short set.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6l2Zp_7SXro?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce comes down with a severe cold and postpones a scheduled show in Arnhem to the next day.</p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>The Wrecking Ball Tour travels down the west coast to Oakland for a show at Oracle Arena. Notables tonight include a rare full-band &#8220;Devils &amp; Dust&#8221; a by-request &#8220;Pay Me My Money Down,&#8221; and a &#8220;Kitty&#8217;s Back&#8221; encore.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bC_Tvu0cDYo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vcvWgNBq7SA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GmThjvWku6U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wJg8MlZUUZs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"46509\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshu