p;ssl=1 997w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /> <img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"46510\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/oakland_tribune_sun__dec_2__2012_-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?fit=805%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"805,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_ (1)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?fit=322%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-46510\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C2411&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"2411\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?w=805&amp;ssl=1 805w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=94%2C300&amp;ssl=1 94w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=322%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 322w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C2443&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=483%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 483w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Oakland_Tribune_Sun__Dec_2__2012_-1-scaled.jpg?resize=644%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 644w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Bruce continues his promotional book tour, stopping at Tattered Cover Bookstore in Denver to meet fans.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DhwHRbF97yQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xu0wDdxscMc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RdBoT8qxApE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2023;\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s scheduled show in Phoenix is postponed to the following March due to his peptic ulcer disease. Instead, he makes an appearance at Darlene Love&#8217;s holiday concert in New York City to present her with a platinum record for &#8220;Christmas (Baby Please Come Home).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QCL9z1FBXFA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Happy birthday to David Sancious, born on this date in 1953. Plus: Bruce debuts &#8220;The New Timer,&#8221; a bookstore appearance in Denver, and more. </p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 70283, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_featu